       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI68301.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI68301.
      *
      *      Expense Reprt - Inserçăo Despesa User
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI68301         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV6830.
       COPY COCV6831.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY TGCL1000.
       COPY TGCL2000.
       COPY TGCK0002.
      *
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME  PIC X(08) VALUE 'COI68301'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CEMPRESA      PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO502'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CFUNCIONARIO  PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO507'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CANO          PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR111'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CMES          PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR112'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CIDPROJ       PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO151'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CIDDESP       PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO021'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CMOED         PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR041'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-CTABELA                   PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NUMERICO                  PIC 9(03).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-NUMERICO.
              10 WS-CODIGO                 PIC X(03).
           05 WS-CCOD                      PIC X(40) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-C2COD                     PIC X(40) VALUE SPACES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI68301         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV6830-MSG.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT   TO COCV6831-MSG.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-DESC-CAMPOS
                 THRU 2100-DESC-CAMPOS-EXIT
           END-IF
           .
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-DESC-CAMPOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-DESC-CAMPOS.
      *
           MOVE '2100-DESC-CAMPOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
      *    IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *    AND COCV6831-XDESCCEMPRESA     EQUAL SPACES
      *    AND COCV6831-CEMPRESA      NOT EQUAL SPACES
      *       MOVE CON-CTABELA-CEMPRESA
      *         TO WS-CTABELA
      *       MOVE COCV6831-CEMPRESA
      *         TO WS-CCOD
      *       MOVE SPACES
      *         TO WS-C2COD
      *       PERFORM 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA
      *          THRU 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA-EXIT
      *       IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *          MOVE TGCL1000-GDESC
      *            TO COCV6831-XDESCCEMPRESA
      *       END-IF
      *    END-IF.
      *
      *    IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *    AND COCV6831-XDESCCFUNCIONARIO EQUAL SPACES
      *    AND COCV6831-CFUNCIONARIO  NOT EQUAL SPACES
      *       MOVE CON-CTABELA-CFUNCIONARIO
      *         TO WS-CTABELA
      *       MOVE COCV6831-CFUNCIONARIO
      *         TO WS-CCOD
      *       MOVE SPACES
      *         TO WS-C2COD
      *       PERFORM 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA
      *          THRU 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA-EXIT
      *       IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *          MOVE TGCL1000-GDESC
      *            TO COCV6831-XDESCCFUNCIONARIO
      *       END-IF
      *    END-IF.
      *
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6831-XDESCCANO  EQUAL SPACES
           AND COCV6831-CANO   NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CANO
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV6831-CANO
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC
                   TO COCV6831-XDESCCANO
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6831-XDESCCMES  EQUAL SPACES
           AND COCV6831-CMES   NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CMES
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV6831-CMES
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC
                   TO COCV6831-XDESCCMES
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6831-XDESCCIDPROJ      EQUAL SPACES
           AND COCV6831-CIDPROJ       NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CIDPROJ
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV6831-CIDPROJ
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA
                 THRU 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL1000-GDESC
                   TO COCV6831-XDESCCIDPROJ
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6831-XDESCCIDDESP EQUAL SPACES
           AND COCV6831-CIDDESP  NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CIDDESP
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV6831-CIDDESP
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC
                   TO COCV6831-XDESCCIDDESP
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6831-XDESCCMOED  EQUAL SPACES
           AND COCV6831-CMOED   NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CMOED
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV6831-CMOED
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC
                   TO COCV6831-XDESCCMOED
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2100-DESC-CAMPOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-VAL-TAB-ART05.
      *
           INITIALIZE TGCL2000-MSG       REPLACING  NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                               ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE WS-CTABELA                TO TGCL2000-CTABELA
           MOVE WS-CCOD                   TO TGCL2000-CCOD
           MOVE WS-C2COD                  TO TGCL2000-C2COD

           PERFORM CALL-TGCP2000
              THRU CALL-TGCP2000-EXIT.

       2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA.
      *

           INITIALIZE TGCL1000-MSG       REPLACING  NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                               ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE WS-CTABELA                TO TGCL1000-CTABELA
           MOVE WS-CCOD                   TO TGCL1000-CCOD
           MOVE WS-C2COD                  TO TGCL1000-C2COD

           PERFORM CALL-TGCP1000
              THRU CALL-TGCP1000-EXIT.

       2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'COCV6831-MSG' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV6831-MSG  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)

              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6831-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV6830-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY TGCP1000.
           COPY TGCP2000.

